\[\mathbf{c} \cdot \mathbf{a} = 2m - \sqrt{2} n \sin \theta.\]Also, $\mathbf{c} \cdot \mathbf{a} = \|\mathbf{c}\| \|\mathbf{a}\| \cos \theta = \sqrt{2} \cdot \frac{\sqrt{2}}{10} = \frac{1}{5}.$  Hence,
\[2m - \sqrt{2} n \sin \theta = \frac{1}{5}.\]Similarly,
\[\mathbf{c} \cdot \mathbf{b} = (m \mathbf{a} + n \mathbf{b}) \cdot \mathbf{b} = m \mathbf{a} \cdot \mathbf{b} + n \|\mathbf{b}\|^2.\]Then $\mathbf{c} \cdot \mathbf{b} = -\sqrt{2} m \sin \theta + 2n = \frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}.$

